Abiodun Olanrewaju, the spokesperson of the institution, confirmed the date to TheCable Lifestyle on Wednesday. The OAU’s 2021/2022 matriculation was earlier scheduled for March 9, 2022, but was postponed indefinitely. Olanrewaju, in a statement, said the management concluded arrangements to proceed on March 14. “The Management of Obafemi Awolowo University, Ile-Ife, Osun State, has concluded all arrangements to hold the 2021 / 2022 Matriculation Ceremony on Monday, 14th day of March 2022,” the statement read. “The ceremony will be conducted between 2 pm and 6 pm that day. “All matriculating students are hereby advised to get in touch with the secretaries of their respective faculties for the collection of academic gowns and the details of other formalities. “We congratulate all new students and wish them outstanding success in their academic pursuits. Ambrose Alli University, AAU Ekpoma Part-time students matriculation ceremony date, and matriculation gown collection and other details for the 2016/2017 academic session has been released by the management of the University. The management of Ambrose Alli University, Ekpoma (AAU) has announced the matriculation ceremony date for the 2016/2017 academic session newly admitted part-time students.… In "Education" Federal University of Technology, Owerri, FUTO matriculation ceremony new date for the 2016/2017 academic session has been made public by the authorities of the school. This is to inform all newly admitted students of FUTO (Freshers) and their sponsors, as well members of the general public of the date for the matriculation of… In "Education" Tasued Matric Ceremony for 2014/2015 fresh students date and venue has been announced. Documents required of all matriculating students has also been listed. All such fresh students are hereby informed. The management of Tai Solarin University Of Education has announced the details of the matriculation ceremony scheduled to usher in… In "News"